  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not now-- I don't kill anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I killed a lot of people, but I don't kill anybody today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, I killed a lot of Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A lot of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "OK, now, what it was-- we was going, we were going to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I became-- I was going to school as a sergeant, sergeant school, to be a private soldier.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they send us to the front-- the whole division, the 385th Division, they send us to the front.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, um--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very far.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, I became-- I came to the front, which it was-- about-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the [INAUDIBLE] section, not far from Lwow, on the border from Lwow.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, um, we was not on the front immediately to start with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We was behind the front to teach more, to learn more about the front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They don't throw you out right away in the front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was on the-- I was-- on the front already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I finished school, and I was already [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is in charge of-- normally of 45 people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had-- you have a V shape, two V shapes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], higher sergeant, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not corporal-- corporal is below that. and [NON-ENGLISH] is in charge of corporal, of sergeant, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, the-- not for myself, but in-- in regular life, from the Russian people, you have about 60% anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The 40% is-- is the people which are more intelligent, which they're going to the high school, to universities.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There, also, you have anti-Semitism, but not so much of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
